de.oaam.model.oaam.allocations

Interface DeviceAssignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeviceAssignmentImpl

    public interface DeviceAssignment
extends OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Device Assignment'. A allocations of a device to a location.

    The following features are supported:

    • Device
    • Location
    • Capability
    See Also:
    AllocationsPackage.getDeviceAssignment()
